Consequence_Description:
The accident resulted in one slight injury: one of the members of the fire crew injured his back while setting up the water cannons.

&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;There was considerable property damage: damage to the facility amounted to 4.3 Meuros. Furthermore, the main units affected (hydrogen processing and reforming) were shut down for several weeks. Lastly, because of the significant damage, the technical refurbishment and mitigation plan for the area affected resulted to be massive. The cost of business interruption came to 1.7 Meuros.


